  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  The study included healthy individuals older than 18 years of age with a&#xD;
             best-corrected visual acuity (BCVA) of &lt;0.1 logarithm of minimum angle of resolution&#xD;
             (logMAR) and no ongoing or prior history of ocular or systemic disease.&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  The study excluded healthy individuals younger than 18 years of age with a&#xD;
             best-corrected visual acuity (BCVA) of &gt;0.1 logarithm of minimum angle of resolution&#xD;
             (logMAR) with ongoing or prior history of ocular or systemic disease.&#xD;
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
